| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6312 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhouse)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 5bba0d4c-5fe6-5505-9f41-9b80601edfe5"
